data.description: Updated Ranch! This cozy 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom ranch is situated on a quiet, tree-lined street in beautiful Dearborn heights! New Furnace (2020), New AC (2020) and so much more! Home boasts large living room with tons of natural light! Great Eat-in kitchen with stainless appliances, built-in hutch and breakfast nook! Large back bedroom with exterior access to backyard! Samsung stackable Washer & Dryer! Outside you'll find the large, FULLY fenced-in yard with private shed and gazebo! Home is just a few blocks away from Shamansky park! Schedule your showing today!
